description:
The CE-IVD DE-M Electronic Single-Channel Micropipette, 0.5-10 µL, with Australia AC adapter, BRAND combines the characteristics of the globally recognized mechanical piston air displacement pipette and the advantages of electronic equipment.
Items supplied: Transferpette® electronic pipette, DE-M marking, supplied with performance certificate, battery, AC adapter, silicone grease.
name: CE VD DE-M Electronic Single-Channel Micropipette
